      • unsubscribe

        CompletableFuture<PlcUnsubscriptionResponse> unsubscribe(PlcUnsubscriptionRequest unsubscriptionRequest)
        Unsubscribes from fields on the PLC. For unsubscribing the unsubscription request uses the subscription handle returned as part of the subscription response item.
        Parameters:
        unsubscriptionRequest - unsubscription request containing at least one unsubscription request item.
        Returns:
        unsubscription response containing a unsubscription response item for each unsubscription request item.
